  <main id="main">
    <section id="overview" aria-labelledby="overview-heading">
      <h2 id="overview-heading">Project Overview</h2>
      <p>This implementation covered GL, AP, AR, CM and Fixed Assets modules for a mid‑sized retail client, aiming to streamline invoice processing, automate reconciliations, and support IFRS-compliant financial reporting.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="modules" aria-labelledby="modules-heading">
      <h2 id="modules-heading">Oracle Financial Modules</h2>
      <article aria-labelledby="gl-heading">
        <h3 id="gl-heading">General Ledger (GL)</h3>
        <p>Configured a multi-segment chart of accounts, automated journal imports, and optimized monthly close processes.</p>
      </article>
      <article aria-labelledby="ap-heading">
        <h3 id="ap-heading">Accounts Payable (AP)</h3>
        <p>Implemented invoice automation, supplier self-correction portals, and discount capture logic.</p>
      </article>
      <article aria-labelledby="ar-heading">
        <h3 id="ar-heading">Accounts Receivable (AR)</h3>
        <p>Streamlined invoice posting, credit control workflows, and automated payment matching.</p>
      </article>
      <article aria-labelledby="fa-heading">
        <h3 id="fa-heading">Fixed Assets (FA)</h3>
        <p>Automated asset acquisition, depreciation, transfer, and disposal schedules.</p>
      </article>
      <article aria-labelledby="cm-heading">
        <h3 id="cm-heading">Cash Management (CM)</h3>
        <p>Implemented bank statement auto-reconciliation and daily cash forecasting dashboards.</p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section id="benefits" aria-labelledby="benefits-heading">
      <h2 id="benefits-heading">Business Benefits</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Invoice processing time reduced from 10 to under 3 days</li>
        <li>Close cycle shortened by 75% through continuous reconciliation</li>
        <li>Improved reporting accuracy with audit-ready journal trails</li>
        <li>Compliance with IFRS revenue, lease, and financial instruments standards</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="accessibility" aria-labelledby="accessibility-heading">
